data.description: Plan to stay awhile, you have been warned, company will never leave!  Multi-level outdoor living areas include a very large main level covered porch,  and wrap deck to gaze at the Sangre De Cristo Mts, Crystal Peak, and green forests forever. The outside living areas include serving areas, a bar, fire pits and a hot tub private enough for your Birthday suit.  The surrounding 10 acres of mitigated forest makes it hard to see any neighbors but hard to believe you are only minutes from town in this hidden paradise. Entry opens to soaring ceilings on the main level, newer porcelain plank flooring in the living, dining, master bedroom and kitchen areas. The eat in kitchen has custom cabinets, a walk-in pantry, and a center island w breakfast bar.  An additional dining area opens to the living room which has a wood burning stove for those chilly Fall and winter nights.  The master bedroom is off the living area, has a walk-in closet, 5 pc bath w a jetted tub, and walks out to the main level deck.  2 more bedrooms, a bath, and a main level laundry complete the main floor.  Lower-level living offers a multitude of uses. Ten ft ceilings and slate flooring complement the rec room that includes in the sale a newer pool table, wet bar, and a perfect place to watch movies, and is just a few steps away to the back patio. 4th bedroom with attached full bath and a den with a 4th attached 3/4 bath in addition to a large room currently used as a office. Quality built This custom home is extremely energy efficient with 12-inch ICF solid reinforced concrete walls, hot water radiant floor heating throughout including the garage, 10 ft. minimum ceilings throughout the home, on demand hot water heater, R/V parking area with electric hook up, insulated and dry walled 8x12 storage shed, radon mitigation system, chair lift on stairs.  Make sure you see the full driveway-drives through the other lot to the road.
